00:14:57,956 --> 00:14:59,837
But other than that, they didn't change very much.

336
00:15:00,237 --> 00:15:04,419
You can see that they chose the same shapes, they chose the same colors, the tiles are

337
00:15:04,439 --> 00:15:05,940
the same size as the ones I did.

