00:15:32,214 --> 00:15:34,656
And so I submitted this board for Hoot Owl Hoot.

346
00:15:35,116 --> 00:15:36,157
It doesn't have any art in it.

347
00:15:36,177 --> 00:15:37,098
It's purely graphic.

