00:28:52,772 --> 00:28:59,939
And when I'm stuck, if I just make myself do the work and play the game over and over,

622
00:29:01,060 --> 00:29:03,681
it will suggest different things to try.

623
00:29:04,201 --> 00:29:05,922
So I'll play it against myself, I'll be like,

