00:29:07,382 --> 00:29:08,883
I can't figure this problem out.

626
00:29:08,903 --> 00:29:10,683
I'm like, you have to play it anyway,

627
00:29:10,723 --> 00:29:12,124
you just have to play it anyway.

628
00:29:12,644 --> 00:29:14,204
And I'll keep playing it against myself

629
00:29:14,305 --> 00:29:17,786
until my brain says, well try this, see if it works.

630
00:29:18,306 --> 00:29:23,128
And so it's just the repetitive playing when you're stuck.

631
00:29:23,768 --> 00:29:24,548
You know, at some point,

632
00:29:25,408 --> 00:29:26,589
I do give up and take a nap.

